metadata.eainfo:
	
		
			Text File {EdiFileName}
			Transfer Function EDI File
			U.S. Geological Survey
		
		
			HEAD
			Header file information containing survey and station collection information.
			U.S. Geological Survey
			
				Header block of information containing survey and station collection content, acquisition date, version, and software used to process.
			
		
		
			INFO
			Descriptive content, or metadata, describing the data collection.
			U.S. Geological Survey
			
				Descriptive content, or metadata, describing the data collection including abstract, data description, instrumentation with equipment identifiers, notes, data collection and processing details including software and other contextual information.
			
		
		
			FREQ
			Data block containing a set of frequencies in hertz (Hz.) It defines the frequency set for succeeding data within that data section which are functions of frequency.
			U.S. Geological Survey
			
			
			{frequencyMin}
			{frequencyMax}
			Hertz
		
		
		
		
			ZROT
			Data block containing a set of rotation angles in degrees used for impedances.
			U.S. Geological Survey
			
			
			{rotationMin}
			{rotationMax}
			Degrees
			
			
		
		{ImpedanceAttributes}
		{TipperAttributes}
		
